deck: Canadian small press, specializing in poetry. Based in Toronto, Ontario. Began in 1965 as "Couch House Press." In 1991 the printing section branched off on its own with Stan Bevington at the helm. When Coach House Books folded in 1996, Bevington resurrected it the following year under the name "Coach House Books."
name: Coach House
